data.description: This picturesque custom property sits nestled on an expansive 2.406 acre homesite at the end of a quiet cul-de-sac street with direct white rock creek access within Lovejoy ISD.  The magnificent estate has been updated and features ensuite bedrooms, generous sized living areas, and private study.  Enjoy dinner and movies at home! Spacious media room offers theatre like experience with silk projector screen, new high end projector, and surround sound speakers. Relax in the extra large pool and spa and enjoy your private wooded backyard! Improvements include: 2022: new custom pool tile and resurfacing. 2021: new pool filter and pump. 2021: new handscraped hardwood floors. 2021: new carpet throughout.
